data.description: ATTENTION ALL FIRST TIME BUYERS AND/OR DOWNSIZERS!!! Classic Chicago All Brick Bungalow on quiet tree lined street is new to the market. This three bedroom, 2 baths with detached 2 car brick garage and fenced yard is located in one of the finest neighborhoods of Chicago's northwest area. The decorative fireplace, original woodwork, built-in cabinetry and kitchen with walk-in pantry are just a few of the charming features. Kitchen leads to a lovely enclosed porch overlooking the backyard having endless possibilities. Add some finishing touches with some TLC and make it your own. Attic and full basement are partially finished. Rec room, workshop, laundry, storage area and half bath in basement. Convenient location to Expressways, Public Transportation, Schools, Parks, Restaurants, Shopping, Grocery Stores and Health Care Facilities.
